:name: Micropython @ LiteX VexRiscv
:description: This script runs Micropython on LiteX+VexRiscv platform (without LiteX BIOS bootloader)

$name?="LiteX+VexRiscv"

using sysbus
mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription @./renode/mini_ddr.repl #Needs absolute path

sysbus LoadBinary @./soc_minsoc_arty/software/bios/bios.bin 0 #Needs absolute path

showAnalyzer sysbus.uart
sysbus.cpu PC 0
